{
  "stem": "5261.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "One was working in the camera room, the other one in the kitchen, and me as a writer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My job was, I have to go to the [NON-ENGLISH] room to make all the the book-- the book keeping of the name of prisoners everyday.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was rather a good job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I could-- I was not so close.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I belonged to the high society, as we called, in the-- in the prison.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Therefore, if I visited my old cell with the 40 prisoners, even with the two Polish guys-- but one was sent to the-- I didn't see it, only the other one.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The Apfelbaum was still there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And all of them-- most-- not [INAUDIBLE] but the Apfelbaum, they congratulated me for this job.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were very glad that I succeeded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And especially Apfelbaum, you see, boy, you are young.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I told you, you will be alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But don't forget about us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I never forget.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I also not forget once the-- I came with some bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I have cigarettes, also.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Because, you see, even in the prison it's like small city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They make the exchange.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I never smoked cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But for cigarettes, like money this was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I could buy a little margarine, some bread, some potato, boiling potato.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I took with me some of this food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I went to the cell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I wanted to give not only to Apfelbaum, but also to some other people, you know, this gay from Torun, this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And there was also-- I had some-- I don't know the name-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Maybe also-- but no gay, he was hetero.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I asked, where is Apfelbaum?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They told me, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a few days ago very ill.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had every day this diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He couldn't use of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He made in the bed.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
